## üì° Transmission Incoming...

**Cipher Vault** is a web-based secure communication platform designed with a "Void/Matrix" terminal aesthetic. It prioritizes user privacy by implementing **Client-Side Encryption**.

Unlike traditional chat apps, Cipher Vault uses a **Zero-Knowledge Architecture**: keys are generated in your browser and never stored plainly on the server. The server acts only as a relay for encrypted data‚Äîit cannot read your messages or see your files.

---

## üñ•Ô∏è Interface Uplink

| Secure Chat (RSA) | The Vault (Storage) |
|:---:|:---:|
